rows.label: qev075303_MSG0001
rows.name: You beat them all? You are very strong![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0002
rows.name: Though Zang Crusher had weakened them already.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_JNK0010
rows.name: Argue

rows.label: qev075303_SEL0011
rows.name: Explain that he didn't even scratch them.

rows.label: qev075303_JNK0020
rows.name: Question

rows.label: qev075303_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Tolba about his connection to Gi Zang.

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0003
rows.name: You are harsh. But maybe my aim was little bit off.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0004
rows.name:
Someday I will be strong Prone.
Defeat them with single blow![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0005
rows.name:
But I need Master for that.
He must teach me many killing blows.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0006
rows.name: ...Hmm? You want to know where Master is?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0007
rows.name:
He was here. Then I found him. Then he ran away.
...He went north.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0008
rows.name: You know Master? I am his top student![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0009
rows.name: ...Or I will be. He is very stubborn.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0010
rows.name:
I searched for him everywhere. High and low.
Finally found him here. But he ran away to north.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0011
rows.name:
Hmm. What to do? Beasts that way are probably
stronger than ones here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0012
rows.name: I heard there is jacul rage there![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0013
rows.name:
Even mighty belgazus would not survive encounter with
such monster.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_JNK0030
rows.name: Warn

rows.label: qev075303_SEL0031
rows.name: Tell Tolba that he should return to NLA.

rows.label: qev075303_JNK0040
rows.name: Taunt

rows.label: qev075303_SEL0041
rows.name:
Tell Tolba that he'd go if he really
wanted to train with Gi Zang.

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0014
rows.name:
You are kind, Earth alien. But I must grow strong.
I must change![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0015
rows.name:
If I run now, I fail. It will be no different than when I
lived in village.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0016
rows.name: You are cruel, Earth alien. But also correct.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0017
rows.name:
If I run now, I fail. It will be no different than when I
lived in village.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0018
rows.name: I must change. I must become strong Prone warrior![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075303_MSG0019
rows.name:
I will become Master's finest student.
Then strongest Prone of all![ST:wait ]
